{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Run the spec-interview-writer subagent for ticket TST-001 to process any interview log and help populate the spec.yaml file with technical details from the PRD.\n\nThe PRD is at aidd/docs/prd/TST-001.prd.md and contains:\n- Q1-Q5 answers about RBAC scope, middleware, frontend stack, audit storage, and sync mechanism\n- User flows for admin role changes, unauthorized access, and live session updates\n- API contracts for mutation APIs, role change endpoint, and WebSocket\n- Data model for audit_log table\n- Acceptance criteria AC-1 through AC-4\n\nThe spec file is at aidd/docs/spec/TST-001.spec.yaml and needs to be populated with these details.\n\nPlease process and return a summary of what was written to the spec."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"tool_TBAXl22JX2s7d4pdFKqa8J3w","session_id":"47d41226-ac75-40b0-ac11-528554f314b7","uuid":"0f592b6b-d9cb-41e9-9cf8-b2472d4c67f4"}
